<h3>Post-Graduate Indira Gandhi Scholarship</h3>
<p>The University Grants Commission provides an incentive for parents to observe small family norm for the purpose of supporting higher education through the scholarships to such girls for the academic year 2009-2011.</p>
<p>The scholarship of any single girl child, being the only child of her parents are eligible under the scheme "Post-Graduate Indira Gandhi Schemes" for single girl child under the initiative of MHRD.</p><hr />
